Puggi: I've prepared a big surprise JUST for you.
Pang: For the sake of my sanity, can you PLEASE tell me what the heck is this thing?!?!
Puggi: Puggi's custom-made super mega ultimate zongzi, of course!

Puggi: I know, I know; you're so touched that you can barely talk, right! 
Can't help it; I take such good care of my mates~
Puggi: Puhahaha! Look, I even have the dragon boat prepared!

Puggi: It's exactly like the festival back in your hometown!
If you wanna cry tears of joy, come do it in my arms. 
Ah, but don't soak the feathers, ok?
Pang: Did you have some serious misunderstandings about what a zongzi is?
Puggi: What misunderstanding? Here, I'll feed you~~
Pang: Never in a million years will you ever get me to eat that thing!
Puggi: Awww~ you don't have to be so modest; we're besties~
Pang: PUGGI! There's a limit to how much I can tolerate your actions!
Pang: Get that squirming pile of unidentified mush away from me, NOW!!!
Puggi: Come on, big guy. Ahhhh~~
